<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gustavus Harvest Festival</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #fef5e7;
            color: #2c3e2f;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #d35400;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #e67e22;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #e67e22;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .event-detail {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            border-top: 1px solid #e67e22;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🌾 Gustavus Harvest Festival 🎃</h1>
    
    <div class="event-detail">
        <h2>📅 Date & Location</h2>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> Coming soon – check back for updates!</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Gustavus, Alaska</p>
    </div>

    <div class="event-detail">
        <h2>🏆 Events & Activities</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Harvest market with local produce</li>
            <li>Pumpkin decorating contest</li>
            <li>Live music and community booths</li>
            <li>Kids' activities and games</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-detail">
        <h2>📋 Schedule</h2>
        <p>Full schedule coming soon. Stay tuned!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="event-detail">
        <h2>🤝 Get Involved</h2>
        <p>Want to volunteer or have a booth? Contact the festival organizers.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Gustavus Harvest Festival – Celebrating community and the fall harvest</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
